  <brief_title>A Trial Of Oral Chloral Hydrate Versus Intranasal Dexmedetomidine For Sedated Abr Exams</brief_title>
  <official_title>A RANDOMIZED CONTROLLED TRIAL OF ORAL CHLORAL HYDRATE VERSUS INTRANASAL DEXMEDETOMIDINE FOR SEDATED ABR EXAMS.</official_title>
